data.description: Welcome to this beautiful family home nestled in the friendly community of Royse City, Texas. This meticulously maintained property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a range of attractive features, it's an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your forever home. It's move-in ready and offers all the comforts you and your family need. Schedule your appointment today! Property sold AS-IS, buyer and buyer agent to verify all info.
